author: Reuters Editorial
title: UK virus models based on many people still going to work
description: Britain's modeling for the spread of the coronavirus through the country is based on the assumption that many people would still need to go to work, England's chief medical officer said on Wednesday.
content:
LONDON (Reuters) - Britain’s modeling for the spread of the coronavirus through the country is based on the assumption that many people would still need to go to work, England’s chief medical officer said on Wednesday.
